<div class="wrap">
  <div class="stats controls-print-hide">
    <div class="stat"><div class="muted">Main cues</div><div id="cueCount" style="font-size:24px; font-weight:700;">0</div></div>
    <div class="stat"><div class="muted">Visible fixtures</div><div id="fixtureCount" style="font-size:24px; font-weight:700;">0</div></div>
    <div class="stat"><div class="muted">Mixed fixtures</div><div id="mixedCount" style="font-size:24px; font-weight:700;">0</div></div>
    <div class="stat"><div class="muted">Hard only</div><div id="hardOnlyCount" style="font-size:24px; font-weight:700;">0</div></div>
    <div class="stat"><div class="muted">Preset only</div><div id="presetOnlyCount" style="font-size:24px; font-weight:700;">0</div></div>
    <div class="stat"><div class="muted">Visible families</div><div id="familyCount" style="font-size:24px; font-weight:700;">0</div></div>
  </div>

  <div class="layout" style="margin-top:20px;">
    <div class="controls-print-hide">
      <div class="card">
        <h2 style="margin-top:0;">Cue List</h2>
        <div class="muted">Klikni na cue a zobrazi se jeho content sheet. U kazdeho cue vidis prehled H a P zasahu.</div>
        <input id="cueListFilter" placeholder="Filtrovat cue podle cisla nebo nazvu" style="margin-top:12px;">
        <div class="sequence-content-controls">
          <label><input id="cueListHardOnlyToggle" type="checkbox"> Only cues with H &gt; 0</label>
        </div>
